    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他认为伊朗是直接核谈判的游戏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-says-he-thinks-iran-is-game-for-direct-nuclear-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他相信伊朗愿意就其核计划进行直接谈判，这是在德黑兰表示愿意通过中介进行谈判的第二天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-says-he-thinks-iran-is-game-for-direct-nuclear-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 21:28:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官权衡鄙视特朗普官员对被驱逐出境的命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/judge-mulls-contempt-order-for-trump-officials-over-deportations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官说，特朗普政府官员违反了他的命令，即立即停止被怀疑是帮派成员的委内瑞拉人的命令，并补充说，他可能会引起他们的蔑视。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/judge-mulls-contempt-order-for-trump-officials-over-deportations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 20:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼看门狗探测有关Houthi攻击的信号聊天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/pentagon-watchdog-to-investigate-signal-chat-on-houthi-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼的监察长将对信号集团聊天进行调查，国防部长皮特·赫格斯（Pete Hegseth）和其他特朗普政府官员讨论了对也门对霍蒂武装分子的袭击的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/pentagon-watchdog-to-investigate-signal-chat-on-houthi-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 18:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在特朗普的角色已经结束，但他的影响力保持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/is-elon-musk-resigning-from-doge-trump-adviser-expected-to-step-back</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）有望退后一职，一旦担任唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的临时顾问的130天期间，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的临时顾问已经失败，但亿万富翁仍将对联邦削减成本的努力产生重大影响，并在正式离开后仍然是特朗普的认罪者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/is-elon-musk-resigning-from-doge-trump-adviser-expected-to-step-back</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:44:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普给中国XI一个赢得关税打击世界的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-gives-china-s-xi-a-chance-to-win-over-world-hit-by-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提高对所有国家 /地区的关税的举动将特别严重打击中国的经济。但这也是在XI赋予罕见的开放，以加深整体关系，包括与美国在亚洲及其他地区的关键盟友。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-gives-china-s-xi-a-chance-to-win-over-world-hit-by-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
